  <summary date="2019-07-30T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Hate Crimes Commission Act of 2019

This bill establishes the United States Commission on Hate Crimes. The commission must investigate and report on the following:

 whether hate crimes have increased; factors that contributed to an increase in hate crimes, if one is determined to exist; policies or actions by law enforcement agencies to reduce the commission of hate crimes; and the impact of underreporting on hate crimes statistics and prevention.</summary>
